==Travel==
*The [[Camulet]] can teleport a player to the [[Bandit Camp Quarry|Quarry]] north-west of Menaphos.
*The [[Pharaoh's sceptre]] can teleport you directly inside the [[Pyramid Plunder]] minigame in Sophanem.
*The [[Rug Merchant]] in [[Pollnivneach]] has a travel option to Menaphos, right in front of the north gate.

